featured_reviews.review_id: The most recent negative reviews need an update. Me and some friends visited as a group of 5 in this small store aware of the negative reviews customers had of being rushed and treated like they have COVID, but all the employees treated us with utmost respect. There was a 20-minute wait but we were a bigger group, and it's understandable that everyone has to wait before going into a small store right now. Although they told us we had a 15-minute shopping window they never rushed us, even as we trickled over into the hour where they had to close either for lunch or to sanitize. Some of us were looking with something in mind, but no specific models, and all questions and concerns were answered as we browsed. They even let me take some pictures, and we finally left once all decisions and purchases were made. If anything, we were the ones rushing a bit so they didn't close too late. So, either the employees read the reviews here and adjusted accordingly, or the reviewers were already being rude without realizing. After leaving, we all praised the employees and completely disagreed with what was said a few months ago. This store lives up to its name and we recommend going if you're looking for sex toys!
